Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:54.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}真实的痛感会迎来明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:59.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}世界拥抱着瑕疵的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:02.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}前往找寻含义的起点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:06.09,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}就算毫无发现的时候也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:10.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:17.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}燃烧生命  仅为今宵
